      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just the lab work, it's everything. my parents, my peers... they all see me as this \"rising star\" and now i'm just a fraud. I haven't slept in two days because my brain won't stop looping through every mistake i've made. it feels like there's no version of the future where i'm not just struggling and failing. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to be able to sleep and not have to wake up to this pressure again. i'm just so done with the constant uphill battle.",
